Fuse Fabric is included in [Fuse ESB Enterprise](http://fusesource.com/products/fuse-esb-enterprise/) if you want production support. 

You can get [Enterprise Support, Mentoring, Training and Tools](http://fusesource.com/enterprise-support/support-offerings/) from [FuseSource](http://fusesource.com/). Please do [get in touch](http://fusesource.com/contact) we'd love to help!

Otherwise you may find the [Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)](faq.html) useful or join the [Community](../community.html).

We love feedback of all kinds; whether it's thoughts, ideas, suggestions or bug reports! 

To submit feedback please use the [Fabric Issue Tracker](${project_issue_url}).

